    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/ee0ecce7ea552dc7ab956fe697aef11f.poster.avif?t=1759324080\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/ee0ecce7ea552dc7ab956fe697aef11f.webm?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/ee0ecce7ea552dc7ab956fe697aef11f.mp4?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><br>这是个严酷无情的世界。<br><br>为了有限的资源人们争得你死我活。强悍的部落、游牧民以及那些匍匐在权力阴影之下的可怜人……全陷入了战争与暴力的死亡循环，为了这片大地上少的可怜物资相互攻伐。<br><br>两个老朋友希望打破这种恶性循环，在一片废墟之上建设天堂。风暴正在酝酿。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/9453ed0f23ef2aa4ac3a50f323533a70.poster.avif?t=1759324080\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/9453ed0f23ef2aa4ac3a50f323533a70.webm?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/9453ed0f23ef2aa4ac3a50f323533a70.mp4?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >即时战略</h2><br>从三个敌对阵营中选择一方，然后开始建设基地，收集资源，招募单位，在战役或对战模式中与其他玩家对战或并肩作战。建筑物与单位可以升级，提高效率和能力。<br><br>悉心组建自己的军队，让传奇英雄率领军队，征服敌人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/a94e630d3948f6465b653e65b20d780b.poster.avif?t=1759324080\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/a94e630d3948f6465b653e65b20d780b.webm?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/a94e630d3948f6465b653e65b20d780b.mp4?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队配合与角色</h2><br>终极团队即时战略玩法，与其他玩家一起畅玩所有游戏模式！游戏有三个角色可供选择，选择角色后可解锁特殊技术，与盟友协作，确定自己团队的战略。或者，您可以使用AI伙伴，根据自己的计划部署他们的军队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/a3be1f69ec94ab860dcdb6cf011c3d85.poster.avif?t=1759324080\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/a3be1f69ec94ab860dcdb6cf011c3d85.webm?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/a3be1f69ec94ab860dcdb6cf011c3d85.mp4?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作战役</h2><br>《A Year Of Rain》的合作战役针对双人小队设计。<br>史诗般的故事情节拥有大量经典角色和地点。征战途中您需要制定策略，逃出埋伏圈，揭露秘密，发动战争，而这一切都可以与另外一名玩家共同完成。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/435ee7a87080207c7c948e198b4d32ab.poster.avif?t=1759324080\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/435ee7a87080207c7c948e198b4d32ab.webm?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/435ee7a87080207c7c948e198b4d32ab.mp4?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人模式竞赛</h2><br>经典对战模式的设计意图是打造一开始就竞争激烈的竞赛。新玩家可以使用内置的建造命令开始游戏，而老玩家则可以使用详尽的竞赛统计数据，进一步改进游戏技能，游戏易于上手，但是难以精通！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/871c7b5975a88f46d0924166e7b4c98d.poster.avif?t=1759324080\" width=620 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/871c7b5975a88f46d0924166e7b4c98d.webm?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/319540/extras/871c7b5975a88f46d0924166e7b4c98d.mp4?t=1759324080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阵营与英雄</h2><br>《A Year Of Rain》世界中有三大阵营争权夺势。每个阵营都拥有三个强大的英雄，领导自己的军队。<br><br>鲁帕家族来自西北方，他们的领袖是野心勃勃的贾迪·鲁帕。他打算占领那些无主之地，自己青史留名，同时为子孙留下一笔遗产。<br><br>亡灵军团。他们的领袖是臭名昭著的列诺娜夫人，亡灵大军就像列诺娜的提线木偶，他们或者无脑服从列诺娜的命令，或者积极践伤害他人的使命，或者终日忍受战争创伤的折磨。<br><br>野帮是游牧民、猎手、部落、被遗忘的和堕落的公民以及独身漫游者组成的联合体。他们选择放逐自己，远离所谓的文明地区。他们中的一部分人是残忍的野蛮人，还有一部分是坚韧的幸存者。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>终极团队即时战略游戏。可与其他玩家一切畅玩所有游戏模式。<br></li><li>战役模式，适合双人体验<br></li><li>2v2对战模式，真正为团队游戏设计<br></li><li>三股阵营：鲁帕家族、野帮和亡灵军团<br></li><li>引人入胜的多层次剧情<br></li><li>风格独特的精致画面<br></li><li>强大的经典英雄，领导自己的军队<br></li><li>配乐由屡获殊荣的作曲家Neal Acree创作</li></ul>",
